column29: Protocols: Total RNA was extracted from leaves of 5-week old sulki1-8, Kas-2 and Ler/Kas-2 NIL plants grown at 14- 16 ºC.  Plants were grown on soil at indicated temperatures under 12 h dark /12 h light cycles and 70 % relative humidity and 120 µmol m-2 s-1 of light intensity. Three biological replicates from at least three independent plants were collected for RNA extraction using TriZol (ThermoFischer).  Libraries were prepared using the Illumina TruSeq Sample Preparation Kit according to manufacturer’s instructions.
